      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems with known analytical solutions (Euler beam bending, Hertzian contact) reproduced within 1% for the element types and mesh densities used in the pedicle screw model.",
      "rationale": "Three benchmark cases (cantilever beam, thick-walled cylinder, pin-on-flat Hertzian contact) were executed and documented. Maximum deviation from analytical solution was 0.7%. SOLID186 and CONTA174 elements verified."
    },
