      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario (F1717 compression-bending, non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw) is the same as the COU scenario; no extrapolation required.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity is co-extensive with the COU: same implant design, same test standard, same loading mode, same QoIs. No interpolation or extrapolation of validation evidence is required. The validation domain fully covers the COU domain."
